# HOMEYIGNORE - Tuya Zigbee Master Branch
# Based on working stable-v5 pattern.
# CRITICAL RULE: NO *.json wildcard ŌĆö it breaks runtime deps.
# CRITICAL RULE: NO *.md wildcard at root ŌĆö Homey requires README.md.
# Only exclude specific dev/CI files, NEVER use broad wildcards.

